snippet.title: Tesla vs Lovecraft Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Releases on Steam January 26th
http://store.steampowered.com/app/636100

Science is not afraid! Intense top-down shooter from the makers of Crimsonland and Neon Chrome. Fight Lovecraftian horrors with the brilliance of Nikola Tesla's science. Tesla-Mech is a war machine of immense power, and it's ready to tear eldritch abominations into pieces!

PS4, Xbox One and Nintendo Switch coming later!
